Relative recall w.r.t.\ use cases provides clear metrics of how a KB is faring downstream, and this is advantageous if a KB is built with a primary use case in mind. This strength is however often also a challenge, since often, KB construction is a longitudinal, cross-functional endevaour [machine-knowledge-survey], where use cases are moving targets.